title: SEND ME YOUR VIDEOS!
body:
I'm going to be posting youtube videos for the best and worst plays that YOU have ever witnessed or played yourself! 

There will be countless montages from all regions, and endless funny videos to help you feel a little better about your inting yasuo {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}} 

Please email me @ Leagueoftiltbusiness@gmail.com

& i'll notify you when the channel is up and running! 

<3 

Please bump this & share it for everybody to contribute!

If the file is too large, upload it to youtube & send me the link so i can download it & upload :) 

Thank you!
